            <path d="M8 0a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v1a4 4 0 0 1-8 0V4a4 4 0 0 1 4-4Zm-5 11a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h4a3 3 0 0 1 3 3v4a1 1 0 0 1-1 1H4a1 1 0 0 1-1-1v-4Z"/>
        </Icon>
        <Description>
            Roles and permissions are managed in your Logto tenant. Connect the Logto Management API to surface a
            consolidated, cross-app view of roles and assignment shortcuts here.
        </Description>
